1
00:00:03,570 --> 00:00:05,472
Hey, sleepyhead. Still faking it?

2
00:00:06,606 --> 00:00:08,040
If you don't wake up,

3
00:00:08,041 --> 00:00:09,109
I'm gonna kiss you.

4
00:00:45,912 --> 00:00:47,580
Come on, let's go for a drive.

5
00:00:58,958 --> 00:00:59,993
What's up?

6
00:01:00,226 --> 00:01:02,061
You've been acting weird since we wrapped.

7
00:01:02,295 --> 00:01:03,935
Was there something wrong with the scene?

8
00:01:12,272 --> 00:01:13,640
Close your eyes.

9
00:01:18,678 --> 00:01:20,180
Hey, sleepyhead?

10
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:22,282
Stop pretending to sleep.

11
00:01:22,816 --> 00:01:23,917
If you don't wake up,

12
00:01:24,751 --> 00:01:26,052
I'm going to kiss you.

13
00:01:38,465 --> 00:01:39,699
Why didn't you kiss me?

14
00:01:41,534 --> 00:01:42,534
Is it because...

15
00:01:42,569 --> 00:01:43,769
Go ask the director!

16
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:45,405
Why didn't the kiss happen?

17
00:01:54,047 --> 00:01:55,247
So that's why you're grumpy.

18
00:01:55,248 --> 00:01:56,649
Because we didn't actually kiss?

19
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,417
No, it's just...

20
00:01:58,418 --> 00:01:59,785
The director is out of his mind.

21
00:01:59,786 --> 00:02:01,454
How could he call "cut" right there?

22
00:02:04,624 --> 00:02:06,092
Come on, let's go demand a retake.

23
00:02:06,392 --> 00:02:08,928
Or we could just practice it right now.
